.DT
query_short
$MUDNAME$ Creator Help
query_short

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
query_short -  This method returns the short description of the room.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
string query_short(string room)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^room%^RESET%^ - the room to return the short description of

.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/handlers/map.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This method returns the short description of the room.  This will return
the short description of named cloned objects as well as attempting to
force the room to load if it is not found in the internal
cache.
.EP

